title: Horse trained by Bob Baffert euthanized ahead of the Preakness
description: A horse of Hall of Fame trainer Bob Baffert was euthanized at Pimlico Race Course in Baltimore on the undercard of Saturday's Preakness Stakes.

title: Woman arrested almost 4 years after newborn baby is found alive in plastic bag abandoned in Georgia woods
description: Almost four years after a newborn baby was found abandoned in a plastic bag in a wooded area, deputies in Georgia have arrested the woman they say is the child's biological mother.

title: Student arrested after bringing AR-15, ammunition to a Phoenix high school, police say
description: Police arrested a student after he allegedly brought an AR-15 and ammunition to a Phoenix high school on Friday, authorities said.

title: Girl, 2, dies after Florida parents 'decided to leave the child in the car', authorities say
description: A 2-year-old Florida girl who fell asleep in her car seat died after she allegedly was left in a hot car on purpose by her parents, authorities said.

title: Pregnant woman and her toddler fatally shot in Idaho, sheriff says
North Carolina’s abortion law means even traveling for an abortion may be impossible for some in the South
description: As lawmakers in North Carolina, South Carolina and Florida work to restrict abortion rights, options for Southern women seeking to end a pregnancy are diminishing.

title: Zelenskyy says peace will be ‘closer’ as he makes dramatic visit to Japan for G7 summit
description: Ukraine’s President Volodomyr Zelenskyy touched down in Japan Saturday for diplomatic talks with the leaders of the Group of Seven nations, hours after President Joe Biden and allies announced a slew of new sanctions designed to impede Russia’s ability to prolong the war.

title: Strange alliances emerge in Tennessee as the GOP governor pushes for gun reform
description: Tennessee Gov. Bill Lee’s decision to call a special legislative session to tackle gun reform has prompted unfamiliar allies to line up behind the GOP leader.

title: Weight loss drugs can lead to muscle loss, too. Is that a bad thing?
description: Can weight loss drugs cause muscle loss? Any significant weight loss can impact lean body mass, but it's not necessarily harmful.

title: Brittney Griner back on the WNBA basketball court after being jailed in Russia
description: LOS ANGELES — Brittney Griner had 18 points, six rebounds and four blocked shots Friday night in her first WNBA regular-season game since being jailed in Russia.
